Title: Rothenberger long reach screw driver set pozi + slotted
Description: Ideal for removing awkwardly placed screws in boilers, this Rothenberger long reach screwdriver set contains two screwdrivers, one Cr-Mo flathead and one S2 hardened steel PZ2. Both screwdrivers have comfy soft-grip handles and magnetic tips for retrieval of dropped screws.

Title: Rothenberger 6 piece euro line screwdriver set
Description: This Rothenberger Euroline six piece screwdriver set includes pozi and slotted screwdrivers manufactured in robust, highly resistant steel with dual-component handles. The set includes 5.5 x 125mm and 6.5 x 150mm slotted screwdrivers, 3.5 x 75mm and 4 x 100mm electricians screwdrivers and no.1 PZ1 100mm and No.2 PZ2 125mm pozidrive screwdrivers.

Title: Rothenberger insulated screw driver set 7 piece
Description: Made of chrome vanadium molybdenum steel, this Rothenberger seven-piece insulated screwdriver set is fully insulated to 1000V. This set includes slotted head and Phillips head screwdrivers along with a live wire tester.
